<h3 class="date"><a href="/2012/jul/23/">&#x27a0;</a> July 23, 2012</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="delving-terry-gilliams-persona" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://hollydgilliam.blogspot.co.uk/">Delving into Terry Gilliam&#39;s personal archive</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Oh man. The comedy nerd in me is drooling.  Terry Gilliam&#8217;s daughter is organizing his personal archives and blogging what she uncovers.  Seeing some of the original bits of card he used for Monty Python animations brings back a lot of memories.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
