<h3 class="date"><a href="/2011/aug/15/">&#x27a0;</a> August 15, 2011</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="comedy-podcast-inside-news-cor" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.nytimes.com/2011/08/15/business/media/comedy-podcast-inside-news-corp-feasts-on-a-scandal.html?src=recg&amp;pagewanted=all">Comedy Podcast Inside News Corp. Feasts on a Scandal - NYTimes.com</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>NYTimes piece on The Bugle, the fab podcast from Andy Zaltzman and John Oliver.  Highlight: The author translating the common emailed cry of &#8220;Fuck you, Chris&#8221; into &#8220;sending Mr. Skinner e-mail and Twitter messages telling him off&#8221;.</p>

