        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.hulu.com/peep-show">Hulu - Peep Show</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Attention Americans with senses of humour (sic): Hulu are now streaming the first series of top-notch British sitcom Peep Show.  You should watch it, because it is bloody funny, and only mildly uncomfortably close to the bone.</p>

