    <div class="well" id="everything-tracy-jordan-said" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.unlikelywords.com/2009/05/18/everything-tracy-jordan-said/">Everything Tracy Jordan Said</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Every line delivered by Tracy Jordan in Season 3 of 30 Rock.</p>

<p>&#8220;Hi. I’m Tracy Jordan. My wife is throwing away some of our old towels. Do you want them cuz they’re out by the trash cans. Now that’s gots to be 30 seconds. Nine? OK, here comes the fun cooker.&#8221;</p>

